The '''Force-cult temple''' was founded by [[Ephant Mon/Legends|Ephant Mon]] on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Vinsoth/Legends|Vinsoth]], after the touch of a young [[Jedi Knight/Legends|Jedi Knight]], [[Luke Skywalker/Legends|Luke Skywalker]], had reawakened the spiritual side of him. He then founded a religion which worshiped [[The Force/Legends|the Force]].

